'''Jasmin Werner IX''' (4533-after 4589) was a Japanese policewoman.

== Early life (4533-4571) ==
Werner was born in Tokyo, Japan. She was the older of two children born to [[Eberhard Werner XV]] and the only born to his ex-girlfriend Saida Hajjar.

In 4551, Werner graduated from upper secondary school.

== Career (4571-4589) ==
In 4571, Werner became a cadet for the Tokyo Metropolitan Police Department.

In 4574, Werner was promoted to patrolman.

In 4577, Werner was promoted to trooper.

In 4580, Werner was promoted to corporal.

In 4583, Werner was promoted to sergeant.

In 4586, Werner was promoted to inspector.

In 4589, Werner was promoted to lieutenant. Her death date is unknown.

== Relationship and child ==
From 4551 to 4552, Werner dated a photographer named Hiroo Takenaka (4527-4589). They had a son, [[Eberhard Werner XVI]].
